              <br>
            </div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-block" onclick="saveSelling(sellingItems)">Submit</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card icon-box">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <p class="card-text">
            <div class="icon-box">
              <h4><a href="">Local Land</a></h4></p>
              Land near you. Contact the owner to offer new deals for their land. <br>[SAMPLE DATA]
